##Automation of site automationtesting e2e tests

##How to run them
Open the folder in VS Code
open a terminal
Then write "npm install cypress"
And the last command "npx cypress open"

##Most used commands:
cy.visit - Redirect to the page to be automated
cy.wait - Set a wait time to perform the next action
cy.get - Pulls the code element I want
click() - Click on the desired element
cy.select - Is used for fields with more than one option
.should('be.visible') - Validate if the element is really there
.type - Write in some field